ZH: 草菅人命，害人害己。
EN: Killing people is like cutting grass with a blade.

ZH: 草菅人命的暴行让人痛心。
EN: It is heartbreaking to see lives being taken so ruthlessly.

ZH: 恶劣的交通安全状况让草菅人命成为常态。
EN: The poor state of traffic safety has made casualties a common occurrence.

ZH: 他的无良行为导致了多场草菅人命的悲剧。
EN: His reckless behavior has caused multiple tragedies with casualties.

ZH: 这种没有道德观念的行为就像是在草地上放火。
EN: This kind of immoral behavior is like setting fire to grass.

ZH: 我们不能再让草菅人命的行为继续下去。
EN: We can't let the acts of killing people continue.

ZH: 让这样的恐怖主义行为继续发展下去，必将导致更多草菅人命的惨剧。
EN: Allowing such acts of terrorism to continue will only lead to more tragic casualties.

ZH: 社会需要更加严厉的制裁来制止草菅人命的行为。
EN: Society needs tougher sanctions to stop the acts of killing people.

ZH: 国际社会必须团结起来，共同抵制草菅人命的恐怖主义。
EN: The international community must come together to stand up against the terrorism that results in casualties.

ZH: 各国政府需要采取更有力的措施来遏制草菅人命的事件。
EN: Governments around the world need to take stronger measures to curb incidents that result in casualties.

ZH: 草菅人命的行为必须被严厉禁止。
EN: The act of killing people must be strictly prohibited.

ZH: 良好的文明道德可以避免草菅人命的悲剧。
EN: Good moral values can prevent tragedies with casualties.

ZH: 我们不能容忍任何形式的草菅人命的行为。
EN: We can't tolerate any form of killing people.

ZH: 保护人民生命安全是政府的根本责任。
EN: Protecting the safety of people's lives is the fundamental responsibility of the government.

ZH: 领导者们应该积极采取措施维护人民的生命安全。
EN: Leaders should take active measures to safeguard the lives of the people.

ZH: 我们珍爱生命，反对一切草菅人命的行为。
EN: We cherish life and oppose all acts of killing people.

ZH: 社会需要呼吁停止一切草菅人命的暴行。
EN: Society needs to call for an end to all acts of killing people.

ZH: 永远不要忘记那些因草菅人命而失去生命的人们。
EN: Never forget those who lost their lives due to acts of killing people.

ZH: 我们要呼吁全社会一起来反对草菅人命的行为。
EN: We need to call on the whole society to oppose acts of killing people together.
